         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot Garden ¶ 15. Oct. 1857 ¶ My dear Dr. Asa Gray, ¶  ¶ I have but a few spare moments left before the close of the mail, to answer your very kind lines just arrived through Sir Will. Hooker...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.10.15</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Asa Gray</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Gray Herbarium Archives, Harvard University, Cambridge, Massachusetts.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">15. Oct. 1857</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Dr. Asa Gray,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have but a few spare moments left before the close of the mail, to answer your very kind lines just arrived through Sir Will. Hookers care.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> I will do my best to furnish sets of Australian specimens speedily for your N. American lovers of Botany and will review my Composite Collection carefully for a set for your own herbarium.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Gray published several papers on Compositae in <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Hooker's journal of botany &amp; Kew Gardens miscellany</seg> and elsewhere of which M would have seen copies.</p>
               </note> For in whose hands could they better be placed?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Accept, dear Sir, the sentiments of my admiration for you and likewise my best wishes for your welfare.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Most obediently yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
